description:
This is the match up we have all been waiting for! A battle of the defeated, a battle of the losers, a battle of two site favorites. We all wanted to see this.

SOMEONE HAS TO WIN!!

Both wrestlers fight to the end, and both never give up or give in. Both try and try in their matches but always end up on the other side of a huge dildo. Which wrestler will get their first win? Which one is the most tired of being a loser? Who is going to finally strap on? The Battle in the Basement is on!!
title: Harmony Rose "The Brawler" (0-6) vs Sarah Jane Ceylon "Blondie" (0-5)
